# Validation and Attributes Test

This sample demonstrates various validation rules and HTML attributes.

## Required Field Validation

@required_text(Required Text): [text required placeholder="This field is required"]
@required_email(Required Email): [email required]
@required_number(Required Number): [number required min=1]

## Length Validation

@min_length(Minimum Length): [text minlength=5 placeholder="At least 5 characters"]
@max_length(Maximum Length): [text maxlength=20 placeholder="Maximum 20 characters"]
@exact_range(Character Range): [text minlength=8 maxlength=16 placeholder="8-16 characters"]

## Numeric Validation

@min_value(Minimum Value): [number min=10 placeholder="Minimum value: 10"]
@max_value(Maximum Value): [number max=100 placeholder="Maximum value: 100"]
@step_value(Step Value): [number min=0 max=100 step=5 placeholder="Increments of 5"]

## Pattern Validation

@phone_pattern(Phone Pattern): [text pattern="[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{3}-[0-9]{4}" placeholder="123-456-7890"]
@zip_code(ZIP Code): [text pattern="[0-9]{5}" placeholder="12345"]
@username_pattern(Username): [text pattern="[a-zA-Z0-9_]{3,16}" placeholder="Letters, numbers, underscore only"]

## Accessibility Attributes

@accessible_name(Accessible Name): [text aria-label="User's full name" placeholder="Full name"]
@described_field(Described Field): [text aria-describedby="help-text" placeholder="Enter data"]
@labeled_field(Labeled Field): [text aria-labelledby="custom-label"]

## Custom Data Attributes

@tracked_field(Tracked Field): [text data-track="user-input" data-category="personal"]
@analytics_field(Analytics Field): [text data-analytics="form-field" data-event="input-change"]

## CSS Classes and Styling

@styled_input(Styled Input): [text class="custom-input highlighted" placeholder="Custom styled field"]
@large_input(Large Input): [text class="input-lg" placeholder="Large input field"]

## Autocomplete Attributes

@autocomplete_name(Name with Autocomplete): [text autocomplete="name" placeholder="Browser will suggest names"]
@autocomplete_email(Email with Autocomplete): [email autocomplete="email" placeholder="Browser will suggest emails"]
@autocomplete_phone(Phone with Autocomplete): [tel autocomplete="tel" placeholder="Browser will suggest phone numbers"]

## Disabled and Readonly States

@disabled_field(Disabled Field): [text disabled value="This field is disabled"]
@readonly_field(Readonly Field): [text readonly value="This field is readonly"]

## Spellcheck Control

@spellcheck_on(Spellcheck On): [text spellcheck="true" placeholder="Spellcheck enabled"]
@spellcheck_off(Spellcheck Off): [text spellcheck="false" placeholder="Spellcheck disabled"]

@submit_validation: [submit label="Test Validation"]
